OL,3,CFire association calls for urgent
OL,4,Cfunding to address lack of PPE and
OL,5,Ctraining
OL,7,FThe States of Jersey Fire and Rescue
OL,8,FAssociation (FRSA) has suggested that
OL,9,F"years of under-investment" could put
OL,10,Fislanders at increased risk.
OL,12,FTim Le Cocq, the FRSA's President,
OL,13,Fwrote to the Home Affairs scrutiny
OL,14,Fpanel during a review into 2026's
OL,15,Fproposed budget to highlight what he
OL,16,Fcalled a lack of investment into the
OL,17,FStates of Jersey Fire and Rescue
OL,18,FService (SJFRS).
