OL,3,CFire association calls for urgent
OL,4,Cfunding to address lack of PPE and
OL,5,Ctraining
OL,7,FWhile the 2026 budget includes a
OL,8,F#413,000 cash boost, rising to #1.3
OL,9,Fmillion over the next three years, Mr
OL,10,FLe Cocq said the government has "not
OL,11,Fadequately invested" in the service.
OL,13,F"For too long, the government has not
OL,14,Finvested in the SJFRS to provide an
OL,15,Fenvironment that appropriately
OL,16,Fconsiders the risk to staff,
OL,17,Fislanders, and visitors," he claimed.
