OL,7,FMr Le Cocq, who is stepping down from
OL,8,Fhis role this week, also wrote
OL,9,F"effective preparation and response
OL,10,Fmust come first and as a priority".
OL,12,FThe President also outlined that
OL,13,Fchange is not enacted quickly enough
OL,14,Fin the island. He lists several areas
OL,15,Fof deficiency, from a lack of
OL,16,Fpersonnel to training.
OL,18,FOne highlight was that recommendations
OL,19,Ffollowing Phase 1 of the Grenfell
OL,20,FTower Inquiry have not been
OL,21,Fimplemented in Jersey.
