OL,5,Ctraining
OL,7,FThe letter also added that investment
OL,8,Finto the Emergency Services Control
OL,9,FCentre could "provide safe systems of
OL,10,Fwork" for firefighters to help them
OL,11,F"save life in a safe and effective
OL,12,Fmanner".
OL,14,FAs part of his comments on the
OL,15,Fproposed Budget, the association
OL,16,Fpresident says the service also faces
OL,17,Fthe challenge of providing effective
OL,18,Fpersonal protective equipment (PPE).
