OL,5,Ctraining
OL,7,FLast month, the Head of the Fire
OL,8,FService warned that there was not
OL,9,Fenough kit to protect firefighters
OL,10,Ffully.
OL,12,FMr Le Tocq highlighted that
OL,13,Ffirefighters are at an increased risk
OL,14,Fof exposure to carcinogens due to
OL,15,Ftheir access to "limited or degrading
OL,16,FPPE".
