OL,3,CFire association calls for urgent
OL,4,Cfunding to address lack of PPE and
OL,5,Ctraining
OL,7,F"Investment in this area is a
OL,8,Fnecessity, but should also extend to
OL,9,Fhealth screening of firefighters, just
OL,10,Fas was recommended by the PFAS Panel
OL,11,Fin relation to the occupational
OL,12,Fexposure to PFAS chemicals in
OL,13,Ffirefighting foams."
OL,15,FThe President also hopes that the
OL,16,Fproposal to increase firefighter
OL,17,Fnumbers is coupled with improvements
OL,18,Fto training and "specialised
OL,19,Fdisciplines".
