OL,5,Ctraining
OL,7,F"Capacity may still be limited when
OL,8,Fconsideration of all elements of the
OL,9,FIsland's emergency response,
OL,10,Fresilience, protection and prevention
OL,11,Fthat are provided by SJFRS, is taken
OL,12,Finto account ` more a stepping stone
OL,13,Fof justified investment toward a safer
OL,14,FJersey."
OL,16,FITV News approached government
OL,17,Fministers with the letter's concerns,
OL,18,Fbut they declined to comment.
